00:01:52.120 --> 00:01:52.920
Lock the ghost.

00:01:52.920 --> 00:01:57.660
In the software world, remove is not always equal to gone.

00:01:57.920 --> 00:01:58.740
Completely gone.

00:01:59.000 --> 00:01:59.960
This is crystal clear.

00:02:00.120 --> 00:02:01.660
