I presented that removed packages could still be...

00:06:45.540 --> 00:06:46.180
I don't know.

00:06:46.460 --> 00:06:46.640
Yeah.

00:06:46.720 --> 00:06:47.420
Well, I mean, there's a lot.

00:06:48.360 --> 00:06:51.080
Security is a big thing.

00:06:51.600 --> 00:06:51.740
Anyway.

00:06:52.160 --> 00:06:52.360
Yeah.

00:06:52.460 --> 00:06:56.580
Supply chain security is extra bad because it's not even necessarily the things that you're using.

00:06:56.660 --> 00:06:59.700
It could be the things that you're using, what they're using, you know?

00:06:59.900 --> 00:07:00.180
Right.

00:07:00.280 --> 00:07:01.360
And something could change there.

00:07:01.360 --> 00:07:04.620
Like, I'm not checking on, I don't know, care debt, for example.

